race.comment: THE BIG FREEZE (4) will go close with a repeat of his big 54 win two back. Forgiving the latest in a 64 and he has the rail today and a 3kg claim. MIRACOLI (1) made good improvement beaten 1L over a mile. The query is the shorter trip but he's going well enough to counter. VITESSE BREEZE (2) threatened twice and then got too far back last time and didn't get into it. Suited in this lineup and an improved effort is on the cards. FAITHFUL CHAMPION (6) didn't have much luck last time in stronger company. He can race more forward and a senior hoop replaces the 3kg apprentice. Deserves consideration.
